# Telecom Billing Dispute Resolution — Environment Variables
#
# No external API keys required for this example.
# All integrations use local MCP servers that ship with Node.js.
#
# The following MCP servers are used and installed automatically via npx:
#   @modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem
#   @modelcontextprotocol/server-sequential-thinking
#   @modelcontextprotocol/server-memory
#
# To run this example you only need:
#   1. Node.js >= 18
#   2. AO CLI: npm install -g @launchapp-dev/ao-cli
#   3. An Anthropic API key configured in AO settings

# Optional: Override the filesystem root for MCP (defaults to project root)
# FILESYSTEM_ROOT=/path/to/telecom-billing-resolver
